INSERT INTO packages (name, slug, description, price, duration, destination, highlights, featured, published) VALUES
('Romantic Escape', 'romantic-escape', 'Perfect for couples seeking an intimate getaway with luxury accommodations and private experiences', 2999, '5 Days / 4 Nights', 'North Malé Atoll', 'Luxury water villa,Private candlelit beach dinner,Couples spa treatment,Sunset dolphin cruise,Airport transfers included', 1, 1),
('Ultimate Paradise', 'ultimate-paradise', 'The ultimate all-inclusive Maldives experience with premium amenities and exclusive island hopping adventures', 4999, '7 Days / 6 Nights', 'South Ari Atoll', 'Premium overwater villa with pool,All-inclusive dining and drinks,Snorkeling and diving excursions,Island hopping adventure,Spa and wellness package,Personal concierge service', 1, 1),
('Island Explorer', 'island-explorer', 'Discover the hidden gems of the Maldives with guided tours and authentic cultural experiences', 3499, '6 Days / 5 Nights', 'Baa Atoll', 'Beach villa accommodation,Daily breakfast included,Water sports activities,Guided snorkeling tours,Cultural island visit,Local market exploration', 1, 1),
('Honeymoon Bliss', 'honeymoon-bliss', 'Create unforgettable memories on your special day with romantic settings and personalized service', 5499, '8 Days / 7 Nights', 'Vaavu Atoll', 'Private overwater bungalow,Champagne breakfast in bed,Sunset cruise for two,Couples massage and spa,Gourmet dining experiences,Photography session', 0, 1),
('Adventure Seeker', 'adventure-seeker', 'For thrill-seekers and water sports enthusiasts looking for an action-packed vacation', 3299, '5 Days / 4 Nights', 'Lhaviyani Atoll', 'Water villa accommodation,Surfing lessons,Advanced diving certification,Windsurfing and kitesurfing,Jet ski rentals,Island jungle trekking', 0, 1),
('Family Fun Paradise', 'family-fun-paradise', 'Create lasting memories with your family in a kid-friendly resort with activities for all ages', 4299, '7 Days / 6 Nights', 'Meemu Atoll', 'Family villa with kids club,Snorkeling for beginners,Marine life education,Beach games and activities,Kids spa treatments,Family dining experiences', 0, 1),
('Luxury Retreat', 'luxury-retreat', 'Experience ultimate luxury with world-class amenities and personalized concierge service', 6999, '10 Days / 9 Nights', 'Dhaalu Atoll', 'Presidential villa with private pool,24/7 personal butler service,Private yacht excursions,Michelin-trained chef,Unlimited spa treatments,Helicopter island tours', 0, 1),
('Budget Beach Getaway', 'budget-beach-getaway', 'Affordable Maldives vacation without compromising on natural beauty and island charm', 1899, '4 Days / 3 Nights', 'Addu Atoll', 'Standard beach bungalow,Shared snorkeling tours,Local island visits,Beach volleyball and activities,Group dining experiences,Airport shuttle included', 0, 1)
